name: SHOCKER
description:
No more mr. nice guy.

Shocker is one those films you watched as a child on Vcd and always remembered it as a cool and interesting slasher movie. Felt like this movie was underrated as a 80s slasher and wanted to watch it again. Seeing it again, it was an odd movie with an awkard chase scene beetwen tv channels, a soundtrack which is way out of place and very mediocore acting. It is a cute and fun experiment and a nice memory from my childhood.
